extendedInfo.description: Prepare to be amazed by an ancient Egyptian mind reading magic act.Pick a number, follow some simple instructions and find a matching symbol in an ancient Egyptian scroll. Do not click on the symbol and do not tell anyone what the symbol is, for the Amazing Mind Reader can reach right into the depth of your soul and retrieve it!With quality graphics, music and sound effects, the Amazing Mind Reader will surely amaze your friends and family. They will have no idea how it is done...
